466
00:30:25,600 --> 00:30:27,158
O que estamos aqui a fazer?

467
00:30:27,360 --> 00:30:28,713
Viemos despedir-nos.

468
00:30:28,920 --> 00:30:31,673
Prometo-te que não voltarão
a magoar-te.

469
00:30:31,880 --> 00:30:34,189
