505
00:32:40,080 --> 00:32:41,354
Agora ajuda-me a mim.

506
00:32:44,040 --> 00:32:45,632
Por favor.

507
00:32:47,440 --> 00:32:49,749
Tira-nos daqui.

508
00:33:02,880 --> 00:33:04,552
